{"tid":711104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民hot talk】 西貢海底撈出相機　好心人曬相尋小學雞","createTime":"2018-06-21T09:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:02:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"580eab9041016749bc5eb5a574c750767e0ed5ed","tid":711104,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180621/20427222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20427222&d=5eA8betqB0%2BzXbXhkNI%2F110Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5f0394f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F20427222&h=0b7575bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180621/20427222</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月21日 <br />\n<br />\n【網民hot talk】<br />\n西貢海底撈出相機　好心人曬相尋小學雞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n石沉大海的相機重見天日！一名網友在潛水時撈起一部陳年相機，發現內裡記憶卡仍未壞掉，當中有不少短片及相片，遂在網上發貼文尋物主，獲不少網民響應，一些fb群組也轉發貼文，一呼百應助找出物主或相中人。<br />\n<br />\n網民Kim Win在「香港一手二手交易市場(必須列價發售)」群組貼文，指早前在西貢白臘灣水底找到一部Nikon Coolpix橙色相機，機面貼有「陳樂澄」名字，更很有心地打印出數張疑似物主的校園生活照，「內有小朋友珍貴劍擊比賽影片及相片，望能尋回物主」。其後另一網民Cammy Ho在《巴打絲打facebook fanclub》轉載，認為有關影片對小朋友十分珍貴，希望大家略盡綿力幫手。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指現時很多小朋友不上fb，較難找到，Cammy Ho就希望女孩家長及認識她的人會看到貼文。網民讚Kim Win好人，又笑言「幫我順手尋埋副rayban，都係西貢」，亦有人指相機今次真正通過防水測試。<br />\n<br />\n早前台灣亦發生類似事件，宜蘭縣的小學生由老師帶領到海灘清潔垃圾時，發現一部被放在密封膠盒的Canon G12相機，記憶卡內亦有不少相片，從中推斷機主應是日本人。該老師透過網絡發佈相片後，收到台灣駐日代表處新聞組通知，表示找到沖繩石垣島一間潛水店，店方正聯絡相機主人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民留言：<br />\n<br />\nAlvIn Lee：幫我順手尋埋副rayban都係西貢<br />\n<br />\nRaymond Wong：防水測試通過<br />\n<br />\nJo Chiu：好人好事<br />\n<br />\nJoe Sit：相機有學生名應該容易搵到  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n追數神器　轉賬毋須戶口號碼<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「天下為公」聘英律師行查UGL案"},{"pid":"75b588e60092f834cca5a4b65beb89afb33775aa","tid":711104,"uid":67238,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"西貢幾時開左海底撈 仲要有相機賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432f8b5df5f7289141bc8d183dd70568df504445","tid":711104,"uid":124537,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e2211f7498488b2d899e1994a30b71a454d6f6","tid":711104,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"432f8b5df5f7289141bc8d183dd70568df504445","tid":711104,"uid":124537,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"正字係咩？"},{"pid":"9bdec4f0d04dbe470c658bec5b2d4597e507f0a4","tid":711104,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"432f8b5df5f7289141bc8d183dd70568df504445","tid":711104,"uid":124537,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"D大陸人真係麻撚煩 又關你D大陸閪舖事<br />\n好人好姐真係唔會諗去呢邊"},{"pid":"4c19c6e9272eb4040698749f593ca5f9d16ed669","tid":711104,"uid":67238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e2211f7498488b2d899e1994a30b71a454d6f6","tid":711104,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"432f8b5df5f7289141bc8d183dd70568df504445","tid":711104,"uid":124537,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:31:23.000Z","msg":"海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"正字係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%BC%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flex